Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:21.70,Main,,0,0,0,,那兩個傢伙要幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.77,0:02:22.64,Main,,0,0,0,,一本正經的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:24.19,Main,,0,0,0,,夜斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.47,0:02:26.55,Main,,0,0,0,,我有話跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:27.94,Main,,0,0,0,,說… 說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:31.18,Main,,0,0,0,,雪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:34.60,Main,,0,0,0,,是不是終於忍不了小夜斗了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.83,0:02:36.15,Main,,0,0,0,,別哭 小福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:37.44,Main,,0,0,0,,是夜斗不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:39.68,Main,,0,0,0,,全部都是他的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:40.92,Main,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.98,0:02:42.44,Main,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:44.18,Main,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:45.27,Main,,0,0,0,,交…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:48.64,Main,,0,0,0,,交到朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:53.56,Main,,0,0,0,,好可愛
